description:
Eternal Evil, a tense and atmospheric first-person survival horror game, launches on Xbox Series X|S. Players step into a city plagued by a supernatural outbreak, managing limited resources, solving puzzles, and uncovering a dual-perspective narrative rooted in classic horror design.
